{"schemaVersion":2,"id":"harness:effort-policy-low-default-escalate-model:op:auto-a9c73f9f51169b7397fa52d5","layer":"harness","key":"effort-policy-low-default-escalate-model","body":"PO 方針 2026-07-19: 最近のモデルは reasoning effort low/medium 既定でよい。それ以上の品質が要る場合は effort を上げるのではなく上位モデルへ振る (effort エスカレーションよりモデルエスカレーション優先)。根拠 = model-bench 実測 (scratchpad/model-bench、K3 max=391s/low=30s で品質同一、Sol は effort 無感応)。src/team/model-effort.ts の標準 effort 見直し (fable/opus=high 据置きの妥当性含む) と adaptReasoningEffort の「浅い→一段上げ」ロジックを「浅い→モデル昇格提案」へ改める検討を要する。","type":"decision","provenance":{"planId":"PLAN-L7-450-state-db-vscode-decoupling","sessionId":"cli-memory","runtime":"human","origin":"po-chat-2026-07-19"},"lifecycle":{"state":"active","expiresAt":null,"consumedAt":null,"consumedBy":null},"links":[],"supersedes":null,"createdAt":"2026-07-18T23:44:11.478Z"}
{"schemaVersion":2,"id":"harness:effort-policy-low-default-escalate-model:op:auto-75a935404b37a9253d2bfd1b","layer":"harness","key":"effort-policy-low-default-escalate-model","body":"PO 方針 2026-07-19 (改訂): reasoning effort は非対称既定とする。上位モデル (fable/opus/sonnet/sol/terra/K3 等) = low/medium 既定、品質不足時は effort を上げず上位モデルへ振る (モデルエスカレーション優先)。下位・軽量モデル (spark / luna 等) = high 既定 (思考量で底上げする価値がある)。根拠 = model-bench 実測 (K3 max=391s/low=30s 品質同一、Sol effort 無感応、spark/luna は判定系スコア下位)。src/team/model-effort.ts の標準 effort レジストリと adaptReasoningEffort の見直し (浅い→モデル昇格提案) を PLAN 化して反映すること。","type":"decision","provenance":{"planId":"PLAN-L7-450-state-db-vscode-decoupling","sessionId":"cli-memory","runtime":"human","origin":"po-chat-2026-07-19"},"lifecycle":{"state":"active","expiresAt":null,"consumedAt":null,"consumedBy":null},"links":[],"supersedes":"harness:effort-policy-low-default-escalate-model:op:auto-a9c73f9f51169b7397fa52d5","createdAt":"2026-07-18T23:45:33.561Z"}
